OL,3,CCampaigner says the underinvestment in
OL,4,Csewers is threatening local development
OL,6,FA water quality campaigner says
OL,7,Funderinvestment in the sewer network
OL,8,Fis now threatening whether new
OL,9,Fdevelopment is possible around
OL,10,FWindermere.
OL,12,FProposals to transform a former water
OL,13,Ftesting laboratory on the shores of
OL,14,FWindermere near Far Sawrey into a new
OL,15,Fhotel have received more than 900
OL,16,Flocal objections, due to concerns over
OL,17,Fthe local water treatment site's
OL,18,F'incapacity' to deal with the current
OL,19,Famount of sewage.
