OL,3,CCampaigner says the underinvestment in
OL,4,Csewers is threatening local development
OL,6,FMatt Staniek, from Save Windermere,
OL,7,Fbelieves developers are unable to
OL,8,F"sustainably develop the area" due to
OL,9,Fthe lack of infrastructure investment
OL,10,Fin water treatment.
OL,12,FHe said of Ferry House treatment
OL,13,Fworks: "It's essentially a cesspit
OL,14,Fwhich is a storage tank. No treatment
OL,15,Fof sewage occurs at this site. There's
OL,16,Falready a known issue where this site
OL,17,Fhas been overflowing.
