OL,3,CCampaigner says the underinvestment in
OL,4,Csewers is threatening local development
OL,6,F"And then the solution that's been put
OL,7,Fforward by United Utilities is that
OL,8,Fthey're just going to keep tankering
OL,9,Ffrom this site to Ambleside Wastewater
OL,10,FTreatment Works, which we already have
OL,11,Fevidence to show has spilled illegally
OL,12,Fin previous years.
OL,14,F"What they said ten years ago in a
OL,15,Freport that they commissioned is that
OL,16,Ftankering from this is not a long term
OL,17,Fsolution."
