OL,3,CCampaigner says the underinvestment in
OL,4,Csewers is threatening local development
OL,6,FSave Windermere says emptying the tank
OL,7,Fseveral times a week, driving the
OL,8,Fsewage to a full treatment works burns
OL,9,Ffuel and is vulnerable to not
OL,10,Fhappening in bad winter weather.
OL,12,FResidents believe proposals to build
OL,13,Fan 18-bedroom hotel could put too much
OL,14,Fpressure on the sewage network, and
OL,15,Fcould then damage Windermere's water
OL,16,Fquality.
OL,18,FThe planned hotel is situated next to
OL,19,FUnited Utilities' Ferry House
OL,20,Fwastewater facility.
