OL,3,CCampaigner says the underinvestment in
OL,4,Csewers is threatening local development
OL,6,FA spokesperson for United Utilities,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have already announced plans
OL,8,Ffor significant investment to upgrade
OL,9,Fnumerous sites to help improve water
OL,10,Fquality in Windermere.
OL,12,F"In the last 12 months we have already
OL,13,Fmade investment in our Ferry House
OL,14,Fsite to increase its capacity. We will
OL,15,Falso be making further upgrades at the
OL,16,Fsite to support any future
OL,17,Fdevelopments, subject to securing the
OL,18,Fnecessary permissions and following
OL,19,Fdue process."
