OL,3,CCampaigner says the underinvestment in
OL,4,Csewers is threatening local development
OL,6,FIn the planning application, the
OL,7,Fdevelopers Mikhail Hotel and Leisure
OL,8,FGroup, proposed installing a private
OL,9,Fsystem to treat the hotel's sewage if
OL,10,Ftheir plans were approved.
OL,12,FThe Environment Agency recommended the
OL,13,FMikhail Group's drainage strategy
OL,14,Fshould be denied.
OL,16,FThe organisation stated: "The lack of
OL,17,Fcapacity or plans to improve capacity
OL,18,Fin the public sewer is not a valid
OL,19,Freason for a development to install a
OL,20,Fprivate sewerage system."
