OL,3,CCampaigner says the underinvestment in
OL,4,Csewers is threatening local development
OL,6,FThe developer has now agreed to
OL,7,Fdischarge foul water to the public
OL,8,Fsewer, but not surface water, at
OL,9,FUnited Utilities request.
OL,11,FSave Windermere's Matt Staniek, says
OL,12,Fthe new development will create
OL,13,Fadditional sewage to what already is a
OL,14,F'major problem'.
