OL,3,CCampaigner says the underinvestment in
OL,4,Csewers is threatening local development
OL,6,FHe said: "This site should be turned
OL,7,Finto a pumping station and it should
OL,8,Fbe pumped to a waste water treatment
OL,9,Fworks that has capacity to be able to
OL,10,Ftreat the sewage down to a point where
OL,11,Fit's not having an impact on
OL,12,FWindermere.
OL,14,F"This is simply the fact that the
OL,15,Fprivate water company hasn't
OL,16,Fsufficiently invested to ensure the
OL,17,Fdevelopers like this can come in and
OL,18,Fsustainably develop the area."
